_sText:
-Literally one of the best bhop map ever made and personally my favorite one!

-This is a modified version of the kz_temple map for kzmod.

-Map never been uploaded on gb so some people will miss this 
masterpiece.

-I am not the map maker of this map. So if someone know tell me and I will key author him!

-Map skill is all about control. More map should have this main idea.

-Some texture are missing after the update about source sdk to hammer.
In the folder I have put the texture, just insert the texture folder in common/counter strike source/cstrike/download/materials

-Map getting run on legit: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JW07cp_GJRg

-Map getting run on auto: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K32s8gchw1o
